{
  "stem": "16395.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in the morning we got up, and we had to stand on the appell until you got you-- you a policeman [? when ?] he took you to the-- to work.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got a little coffee, and a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I ate from [? two ?] [? pounds. ?] Every place wasn't anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I think you got used to it by then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think your inside was so strong that you didn't even need this either.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People went to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everybody had their machines.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I worked-- my machine when I was making ammunition.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It really was a very important machine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I learned it very fast, and I didn't make any schmutz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Any schmutz, they called it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't any [? wrongs ?] in it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if you made a lot, they took you away from it, and you never-- they never saw you again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were there for a long time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At night, when we went out when the work was finished, around 5 o'clock they took us back to the barracks, and we washed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we could go out socialize, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "See the men.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A lot of them I know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I already knew my husband-- my husband what he is now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we talked--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We talked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No husbands and wives.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They weren't such really people that old they should be married.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were all young people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Young, I mean 17, 16, 18, 19.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Very seldom, unless-- I don't know, they were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, there were a few older people, too, but they were already there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But from the people what I came from were all young people, very young people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- [SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
